    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with documented justification. Grid convergence index of 1.8% and maximum validation error of 4.1% provide high confidence in RH index predictions. The relative hemolysis index satisfies RH < 1 at all five operating points. The credibility body of evidence, including the hemolysis exposure integral methodology described in the supporting literature, supports acceptance of the computational model for the stated COU.",
